{"TopicId":211327,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"KSP on Epic is only in English. This could be a problem for new players who dont know how to speak/read english.","CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-05T21:37:27Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-05T21:37:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u00A0 uninstalled KSP on my epic app. Changed to Russian on the epic app (at least I think it was). Reinstalled KSP and its still in English.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat indicated that other languages might be possible was that the main KSP game is actually sitting inside a folder called \u0022English\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyone know how to change the language or is it currently impossible?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ghostii_Space","CreatedById":218794,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-05T21:53:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey there! We\u0027re working on getting the other languages uploaded, and we don\u0027t have an ETA yet, but it should hopefully be resolved soon!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-05T22:27:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224215977\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211327\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221672955600\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022218794\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ghostii_Space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n33 minutes ago, Ghostii_Space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey there! We\u0027re working on getting the other languages uploaded, and we don\u0027t have an ETA yet, but it should hopefully be resolved soon!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the update \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T10:32:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224215971\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211327\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221672954647\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161238\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Anth12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Anth12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u00A0 uninstalled KSP on my epic app. Changed to Russian on the epic app (at least I think it was). Reinstalled KSP and its still in English.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat indicated that other languages might be possible was that the main KSP game is actually sitting inside a folder called \u0022English\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyone know how to change the language or is it currently impossible?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDown in either the Russian or Japanese international sub forum, there is a comment on how to do this I think. \u00A0 Posted within the last 24 hours. \u00A0 Alas, you\u2019ll have to manually translate anything recent to figure it out. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T13:40:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216094\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211327\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673001155\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDown in either the Russian or Japanese international sub forum, there is a comment on how to do this I think. \u00A0 Posted within the last 24 hours. \u00A0 Alas, you\u2019ll have to manually translate anything recent to figure it out. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022224544\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed331952187\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/211324-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%BA-%D0%B2%D0%BA%D0%BB%D1%8E%D1%87%D0%B8%D1%82%D1%8C-%D1%80%D1%83%D1%81%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%B9-%D1%8F%D0%B7%D1%8B%D0%BA/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:172px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s a French entry which is already taken care of and the Russian one that is above which I translated and responded to which points back at this post (using google translate). No fix as far as I could find.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do know of a possible fix. Take the language packs from KSP on other platforms like steam/gog/KSP Store but I doubt Private Division would like that option from a legal perspective.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will note that English is my only language. Someone notified me of this issue and my bug hunting persona took over to try to figure it out and so I reported it here and on the KSP bug tracker.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems like an important issue or I wouldn\u0027t have said anything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-01-06T13:43:27Z\u0022 title=\u002201/06/2023 01:43  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 6, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Anth12\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PsiCho_0","CreatedById":224577,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T16:09:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022224577\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5326055274\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/211324-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%BA-%D0%B2%D0%BA%D0%BB%D1%8E%D1%87%D0%B8%D1%82%D1%8C-%D1%80%D1%83%D1%81%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%B9-%D1%8F%D0%B7%D1%8B%D0%BA/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=4216129\u0026amp;embedComment=4216129\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022 style=\u0022height:219px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dsRnGtr_GGE\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dsRnGtr_GGE\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0423 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u0437\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0431\u043E\u0442\u0430\u043B\u043E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-01-06T16:10:07Z\u0022 title=\u002201/06/2023 04:10  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 6, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by PsiCho_0\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T17:56:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216189\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211327\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673021368\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022224577\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PsiCho_0\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, PsiCho_0 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dsRnGtr_GGE\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dsRnGtr_GGE\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0423 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u0437\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0431\u043E\u0442\u0430\u043B\u043E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRussian:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u042D\u0442\u043E \u043A\u043E\u043F\u0438\u044F \u0444\u0430\u0439\u043B\u0430 \u0440\u0443\u0441\u0441\u043A\u043E\u0439 \u043B\u043E\u043A\u0430\u043B\u0438\u0437\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 \u0438\u0437 GOG-\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0441\u0438\u0438 KSP. \u042D\u0442\u043E \u0440\u0430\u0431\u043E\u0442\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0442\u043E\u043B\u044C\u043A\u043E \u0432 \u0442\u043E\u043C \u0441\u043B\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0435, \u0435\u0441\u043B\u0438 \u0432\u0435\u0441\u044C \u0444\u0430\u0439\u043B rar \u0432\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0432\u043B\u0435\u043D \u043D\u0435\u043F\u043E\u0441\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043D\u043D\u043E \u0432 \u043E\u0441\u043D\u043E\u0432\u043D\u0443\u044E \u043F\u0430\u043F\u043A\u0443 KSP, \u043F\u043E\u0442\u043E\u043C\u0443 \u0447\u0442\u043E buildID64.txt \u0441\u043E\u043E\u0431\u0449\u0430\u0435\u0442 KSP, \u043D\u0430 \u043A\u0430\u043A\u043E\u043C \u044F\u0437\u044B\u043A\u0435 \u043E\u043D \u043D\u0430\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0441\u044F. \u0412 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0442\u0438\u0432\u043D\u043E\u043C \u0441\u043B\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0435 \u044D\u0442\u043E \u043D\u0435 \u0441\u0440\u0430\u0431\u043E\u0442\u0430\u0435\u0442. \u041D\u0435 \u0443\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0435\u043D \u0432 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0431\u043B\u0435\u043C\u0430\u0445 \u0441 \u043A\u043E\u043F\u0438\u0440\u0430\u0439\u0442\u0438\u043D\u0433\u043E\u043C, \u0443\u0447\u0438\u0442\u044B\u0432\u0430\u044F, \u0447\u0442\u043E \u043E\u043D \u0432\u0437\u044F\u0442 \u0438\u0437 \u043A\u043E\u043F\u0438\u0438 KSP, \u0430 \u0437\u0430\u0442\u0435\u043C \u0440\u0430\u0437\u043C\u0435\u0449\u0435\u043D \u0432 \u0418\u043D\u0442\u0435\u0440\u043D\u0435\u0442\u0435.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnglish:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a copy of the Russian localization file from a GOG version of KSP. It only works if the entire rar file is pasted directly into the KSP main folder because the buildID64.txt tells KSP what language it is. Otherwise it wont work. Not sure of the copywrite issues here considering its taken from a copy of KSP and then posted online.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut it is a work around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sitte I. von Strolch","CreatedById":224607,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-16T13:04:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/218794-ghostii_space/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=https%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F211327-ksp-on-epic-is-only-in-english-this-could-be-a-problem-for-new-players-who-dont-know-how-to-speakread-english%252F%2526_fromLogin%253D1\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/218794-ghostii_space/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 title=\u0022Go to Ghostii_Space\u0027s profile\u0022\u003EGhostii_Space\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224215977\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211327\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221672955600\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022218794\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ghostii_Space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/5/2023 at 10:53 PM, Ghostii_Space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey there! We\u0027re working on getting the other languages uploaded, and we don\u0027t have an ETA yet, but it should hopefully be resolved soon!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny news about an ETA ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0060t be such a problem to integrate already translated language packs, could it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sitte I. von Strolch","CreatedById":224607,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T03:00:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224215977\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211327\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221672955600\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022218794\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ghostii_Space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/5/2023 at 10:53 PM, Ghostii_Space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey there! We\u0027re working on getting the other languages uploaded, and we don\u0027t have an ETA yet, but it should hopefully be resolved soon!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... Soon\u2122 ... 7 1/2 weeks later...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EI know about this kind of soon...\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ch1\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.urbandictionary.com/define.php?term=soon\u002B%28tm%29\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Esoon (tm)\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/h1\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDescribes something that we are told is coming soon (game updates, TV shows, etc.) but we have heard it enough times to know better. Whoever is saying x event will occur soon is considered to own the trademark on the word because they have used it so many times.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EOr\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://wowwiki-archive.fandom.com/wiki/Soon\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESoon\u2122\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003ESoon\u2122\u003C/b\u003E: Copyright pending 2004-2023 Blizzard Entertainment, Inc. All rights reserved. \u0022Soon\u2122\u0022 does not imply any particular date, time, decade, century, or millennia in the past, present, and certainly not the future. \u0022Soon\u0022 shall make no contract or warranty between Blizzard Entertainment and the end user. \u0022Soon\u0022 will arrive some day, Blizzard does guarantee that \u0022soon\u0022 will be here before the end of time. Maybe. Do not make plans based on \u0022soon\u0022 as Blizzard will not be liable for any misuse, use, or even casual glancing at \u0022soon.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kpi","CreatedById":228325,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-30T00:26:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUntil \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003ESoon\u003Cb style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\u2122\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0day arrives, you might want to try this workaround:\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/Apofoo/KSP-Localization\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/Apofoo/KSP-Localization\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}